article_title: Bobby Jindal Accuses Hillary Clinton Of Health Care Flip-Flop
article_text: Louisiana Gov. Bobby Jindal has attacked potential presidential contender Hillary Clinton for supporting the individual mandate of Obamacare when two decades ago she testified against it.
